Lyra, the Pseudodragon:
Size: Small
Armor Class: 13
Hit Points: 10
Speed: 15 ft., fly 60 ft.
Skills: Perception +3, Stealth +5, Attack Rolls +1
Senses: Blindsight 10 Ft., Darkvision 60 Ft., Passive Perception 13
Languages: Understands Common and Draconic but can't speak
Keen Senses: Lyra has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on sight, hearing, or smell.
Magic Resistance: Lyra has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects.
Improved Telepathy: Lyra can magically communicate simple ideas, emotions, and images telepathically with any creature within 200 ft. of it that can understand a language.

Other: Carries around a brilliant sapphire gifted to her by Verbana for a job well done.
